Detailed Description

Parameters:
ProfileID 
  • 1 to 16 for 3GPP profile
  • 101 to 106 for 3GPP2 profile
ProfileType 
  • Identifies the technology type of the profile
    • 0x00 - 3GPP
    • 0x01 - 3GPP2
    • NULL is not allowed
curProfile 
  • Contains Union of profile(3GPP/3GPP2) structures
